descriptionHtml: [color=#9900ff][size=5]A Cbbe Bodyslide Preset I have made with a slender body and extra large breasts. And unlike my previous presets doesnt need or use any expanded sliders from other mods. So it can be used on any bodyslide outfit. If you want to use it you will need cbbe and bodyslide. Dont use NMM to install. Just download the file manually, unzip, and place the xml file in your body slide preset folder. (skyrim>data>calientetools>bodyslide>sliderpresets) If after installing you do not see the deeja preset in bodyslide select the cbbe standard body under the outfit list in bodyslide and then look under the preset list and select deeja and save the preset to all of the outfits you wish to use it on. Works with any bodyslide compatible mod and HDT. All pictures shown are 0 weight. 100 weight is slightly thicker in the breasts and behind.Â [/size][/color]
